data.description: Great condo end unit on a quiet cul-de-sac in a beautiful area of homes.  Convenient one level living with 3 full baths and finished family room.  6'x24' custom walk in closet in lower level provides an abundance of storage.  The 2 car garage has good storage and is very clean.  Private, awning covered deck is just off the living area.  Updated roof, windows and sliding door. 2nd bedroom was used as an office area and has a full bath and closet.  Very clean and move in ready. New 200 AMP elec. box.
